            Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap<br>
            Backend: Node.js, Express.js <br>
            Templating Engine: EJS (Embedded JavaScript)<br>
            Database: MongoDB (for storing articles and comments)
        </p>

        <h5 class="page-minisubheading-11"> Hosting</h5>
        <p class="hosting-paragraph">
            CodeCrafters Hub is hosted locally
        </p>
